Read and follow CONTRIBUTING.md — it contains the full project context, architecture, and rules.

CRITICAL: Always sync with GitHub first.
This project is worked on from multiple devices. Before ANY work:
1. Run `git pull origin main`
2. Make changes
3. Commit + push when done — never leave uncommitted work

Quick Reference:
- Stack: Python 3.11, FastAPI, Jinja2, vanilla JS/CSS
- Main template: app/templates/dashboard_tv.html
- Styles: app/static/dashboard.css (light/dark themes, 3 responsive breakpoints)
- Routes: app/main.py
- Hosting: Render.com free tier, auto-deploys from GitHub
- Public site is read-only — no user accounts, no personal data exposed
- Never expose model names or mention AI/agents in public-facing content
- Color palette: Bull #3BE8B0, Bear #FD636B, Accent #1BAFD0, Amber #FFB900
